text.section:
A registered pharmacy technician periodically may renew a pharmacy technician's registration for an additional 2-year term, if the registered pharmacy technician:
Otherwise is entitled to be registered as a pharmacy technician;
Submits to the Board a renewal application on the form that the Board requires;
Meets the continuing education requirements set by the Board under this section; and
Pays to the Board a renewal fee set by the Board.
